# Regulatory Compliance & RegTech

This collection focuses on **Using AI for automated KYC, bias detection in lending, and regulatory report parsing.**.

## Notebooks

- 01_automated_kyc_document_classification.ipynb
- 02_regulatory_report_parsing_nlp.ipynb
- 03_compliance_breach_detection_oss_logs.ipynb
- 04_fair_lending_bias_detection.ipynb
- 05_insider_trading_pattern_recognition.ipynb
- 06_gdpr_pii_data_masking_ai.ipynb
